msgctxt ""
"TextAutoFitToSize.xhp\n"
"par_id971708794433499\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select a text box and choose <menuitem>Shrink text on overflow</menuitem>."
msgstr "ເລືອກກ່ອງຂໍ້ຄວາມ ແລ້ວເລືອກ <menuitem>ຫຍໍ້ຂໍ້ຄວາມເມື່ອລົ້ນຂອບ</menuitem>."

